@startuml Manage_Equipment_Issues_State_Diagram
title Manage Equipment Issues - State Diagram
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Pending : Create issue report

Pending --> InProgress : Start handling issue
InProgress --> Resolved : Resolve issue
Pending --> Resolved : Resolve directly

Resolved --> InProgress : Reopen issue
InProgress --> Pending : Put issue back to pending

Pending --> Deleted : Delete issue record
InProgress --> Deleted : Delete issue record
Resolved --> Deleted : Delete issue record

Deleted --> [*]

@enduml
